1
00:01:03,770 --> 00:01:05,900
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,220 --> 00:01:09,830
[Episode 10]

3
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:12,650
After last night's

4
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,760
chaos in the palace,

5
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,760
as his mother,

6
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:18,039
I have to

7
00:01:18,350 --> 00:01:21,000
see for myself today
that the Emperor is safe.

8
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,950
If you dare stop me again,

9
00:01:22,950 --> 00:01:25,480
it will be taken as hiding his injuries.

10
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,890
And that crime means

11
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,680
the extermination of three generations!

12
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,350
Quite lively

13
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:32,039
this early, isn't it?

14
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:52,310
Good morning, Mother.

15
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,479
It's rare for you to come see me.

16
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:03,230
Though in this state,

17
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,790
I suppose I'm rather embarrassing.

18
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,150
What is it?

19
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,150
You see that I'm alive and well,

20
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,400
yet you look disappointed.

21
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,430
How could I be?

22
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:21,470
As long as Your Majesty is safe,

23
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,630
I can rest easy.

24
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:26,710
I'm fine.

25
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:31,560
But my cousin may not be.

26
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:35,560
Xun Simo forced his way
into the bedchamber with soldiers

27
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:38,190
a crime punishable by death
for nine generations.

28
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:41,710
But for your sake,

29
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:44,240
I only stripped the Xun family of power

30
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,870
and punished him alone.

31
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:55,960
Traitors deserve death.

32
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,310
But if Your Majesty insists on fairness,

33
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:02,360
Jiang Li, betrothed as she was,

34
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:05,710
entered the palace and behaved
disgracefully with Your Majesty.

35
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:07,430
She violated propriety

36
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:10,150
and disgraced the royal house.

37
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:13,630
She should be punished today as well.

38
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,560
Very well.

39
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,430
If that's the case,

40
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:36,680
Jiang Li helped me
suppress the rebels last night.

41
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,560
This is a great merit.

42
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,680
I have admired her for a long time.

43
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,240
On an auspicious day,

44
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,310
I will make her my empress

45
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:57,070
Now, have I made myself clear enough,

46
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,280
Mother?

47
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:26,970
Just now, the Empress Dowager

48
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:30,520
was trying to use you to pressure me
into letting Xun Simo go.

49
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:33,070
That was only a stopgap.

50
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:40,230
About making me Empress,

51
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,750
I hope you will reconsider.

52
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:45,510
What if I told you

53
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,830
I meant every word?

54
00:05:17,410 --> 00:05:21,190
♪ One last thread of longing ♪

55
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:25,550
♪ Forgetting what regret feels like ♪

56
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:30,150
♪ Letting time lie to us ♪

57
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:34,340
♪ Turning over in the hands of fate ♪

58
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:39,020
♪ The past that lives in my heart ♪

59
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:43,830
♪ Is your quiet unease ♪

60
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:46,270
♪ If life's answer ♪

61
00:05:46,650 --> 00:05:48,370
♪ Is incomplete ♪

62
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:51,600
♪ Then let me walk what's left with you ♪

63
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,470
You're Jiu?

64
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:53,510
♪ Desert winds, sand filling the sky ♪

65
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:54,960
When the uprising happened...

66
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:55,870
♪ Not even that could erase this ♪

67
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:57,360
If Aunt Liu

68
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:57,880
hadn't taken me away,

69
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,950
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

70
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:01,160
I would've died in that rebellion.

71
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,270
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

72
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,270
But, Li...

73
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,560
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

74
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,160
Those days were brief...

75
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,310
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

76
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:09,800
but they were
the happiest time of my life.

77
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,910
♪ You held the fire
you lit with your heart ♪

78
00:06:13,250 --> 00:06:15,410
♪ And gave it to me without fear ♪

79
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:16,480
♪ Even in the dead of night ♪

80
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,120
So you knew all along...

81
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:20,160
♪ That flash of light ♪

82
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,570
and chose not to tell me?

83
00:06:20,570 --> 00:06:24,510
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

84
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,190
Xie Jiuzhao.

85
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,750
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

86
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:28,120
Do you know…

87
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,510
after my mother took you away
from Chunliu Garden,

88
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:34,390
she never came back?

89
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,570
I waited.

90
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:37,190
♪ The desert in the wilderness ♪

91
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,480
And I kept waiting.

92
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,870
Every single day.

93
00:06:40,909 --> 00:06:41,950
♪ You were there for me ♪

94
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:44,360
Whenever I saw a carriage
pass Chunliu Garden,

95
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,690
I thought it was her,
coming to take me home.

96
00:06:45,690 --> 00:06:49,480
♪ The turbulent night ♪

97
00:06:49,970 --> 00:06:50,510
♪ The intersection of life and death ♪

98
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,190
But I grew up…

99
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,950
♪ The color of my dream ♪

100
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:58,159
And she never returned.

101
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:01,430
♪ We fell in love with each other ♪

102
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,630
Xie Jiuzhao.

103
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,270
♪ I missed you so much ♪

104
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,800
Tell me.

105
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,000
♪ And I can't get you off my mind ♪

106
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,070
How did my mother die?

107
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:11,480
♪ I can't breathe without you ♪

108
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:11,980
Back then...

109
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,860
♪ Sandstorms filled the desert sky ♪

110
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:15,160
♪ Yet they never buried this ♪

111
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,130
Aunt Liu died protecting me.

112
00:07:17,130 --> 00:07:20,460
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

113
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,700
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

114
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,160
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

115
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:26,630
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

116
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,720
Stay away!

117
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,000
Jiuzhao, it's me.

118
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,340
♪ You held the fire
you lit with your heart ♪

119
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:32,610
It's okay.

120
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:33,190
♪ And gave it to me without fear ♪

121
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,600
I'm here to save you.

122
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,210
♪ Even in the dead of night ♪

123
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:36,750
♪ That flash of light ♪

124
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,430
Let's go.

125
00:07:39,970 --> 00:07:41,310
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

126
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:43,710
Right after I got back
from Chunliu Garden,

127
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:44,360
I learned that Aunt Liu had been killed.

128
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:47,440
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

129
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:50,090
♪ Sandstorms filled the desert sky ♪

130
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:50,390
Li...

131
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:53,080
♪ Yet they never buried this ♪

132
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:55,510
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

133
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,630
Xie Jiuzhao.

134
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,900
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

135
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,480
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

136
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,650
I don't belong here.

137
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:05,190
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

138
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,130
Please let me go.

139
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:08,340
♪ You held the fire
you lit with your heart ♪

140
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,610
♪ And gave it to me without fear ♪

141
00:08:11,370 --> 00:08:12,410
♪ Even in the dead of night ♪

142
00:08:12,690 --> 00:08:15,630
♪ That flash of light ♪

143
00:08:16,180 --> 00:08:20,010
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

144
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:24,560
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

145
00:08:25,730 --> 00:08:36,789
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

146
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,390
You can go now.

147
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,000
Take a look. Little trinkets.

148
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,670
Miss, have a look.

149
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:49,440
Son, look. What's that?

150
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,530
Come on, let's check it out.

151
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,440
Hi,

152
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:54,480
do you like this one?

153
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,080
Let me see.

154
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,720
Look,

155
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,150
do you like it, dear?

156
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:04,150
What kind of people were your parents?

157
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:09,910
Let's go.

158
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:10,550
Take care.

159
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:13,210
I can hardly remember
my father's face anymore.

160
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:15,760
I only remember how busy he always was.

161
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,550
I kept waiting for the day

162
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:20,550
he'd have time to talk with me.

163
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:25,120
As for my mother,

164
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,870
she never said it,

165
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:30,200
but I knew she blamed me.

166
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:38,360
No mother truly hates her own child.

167
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,480
She just didn't know

168
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,150
how wonderful my Zhao

169
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:43,720
really was.

170
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,910
Not better than my Li.

171
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:52,440
Li.

172
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,200
Zhao.

173
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:56,630
The days when you are with me

174
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,750
are the best days of all.
